## üñºÔ∏è Image Management

### Image Sources

All images in the templates use Unsplash URLs. For production:

1. **Download images** from the Unsplash URLs used in HTML
2. **Optimize images** using tools like:
   - TinyPNG (https://tinypng.com)
   - ImageOptim (Mac)
   - Squoosh (https://squoosh.app)

3. **Save to folders**:
   - Platform images ‚Üí `images/platforms/`
   - Team photos ‚Üí `images/team/`
   - Project images ‚Üí `images/projects/`
   - Icons ‚Üí `images/icons/`

4. **Update image paths** in HTML:
   ```html
   <!-- Change from: -->
   <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/..." alt="...">
   
   <!-- To: -->
   <img src="images/platforms/image-name.jpg" alt="...">
   ```

### Image Optimization Tips

- Use WebP format for better compression
- Resize images to actual display size
- Use lazy loading: `<img loading="lazy" ...>`
- Compress images to reduce file size
- Use appropriate image dimensions

